title_bed_bats_review: Rental unit in Sylhet · 3 bedrooms · 3 beds · 3 baths
listing_description:
This modern and newly refurbished flat is in the heart of Upashahar next to Rose View Hotel and lots of shops.

3 double bedrooms and 1 servants quarter with private free parking too. 

The whole group will enjoy easy access to everything from this centrally located place.

Each room has its own ensuite bathroom and the furniture is top quality too. Enjoy your stay, stress free in style.
